#--------------------------------------------------------------------
#--------------------------------------------------------------------
#--------------------------------------------------------------------
Use this code to:
1) prepare new fake rates
2) apply the fake rates to the Wjets sample to check validity

#--------------------------------------------------------------------
#--------------------------------------------------------------------
For 1):

I)   root doFakeDet.C
        this produces fake rates in each QCD bin, all store in the 
        file fakeRatesFull.root

II)  root -b -q -l prepareFakeRateHistograms.C
        this merges the QCD bins with proper weighting. Result is 
        again stored in fakeRatesFull.root

III) root  -b -q -l makeFakeRatePlots.C
        this divides the numerator and denominator histograms and 
        sets the names expected by the Wjet test code. Result is 
        stored in fakeRates.root

#--------------------------------------------------------------------
#--------------------------------------------------------------------
For 2):

I)   root doFakeTest.C
        This produces myWHist_elt_0.root and myWHist_elt_2.root
        _0 contains the observerd fake electrons in Wjets
        _2 contains the predicted fake electrons in Wjets

II)  root makeFakeRateWjetTestPlots.C
        This displays a few of the comparison histograms 
        in pT, eta, nJet

#--------------------------------------------------------------------
#--------------------------------------------------------------------
#--------------------------------------------------------------------
